Test Case 6: Add Review
Test Case ID: TC_ADD_REVIEW_01
Description: Test adding a review for a purchased item.
Preconditions: User must have purchased items.
Steps:
Open the "Purchased Items" tab.
Click on the "Add Review" button for a purchased item.
Enter a rating and a comment.
Click on the "Submit Review" button.
Expected Result:
The review is added successfully and appears in the seller's reviews.
A success message "Review submitted successfully" is displayed.
Actual Result:
The review is added successfully and appears in the seller's reviews.
